		<title>Mapping an Industrial Dispute</title>
		<link>https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2017/07/mapping-an-industrial-dispute.html</link>
					<comments>https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2017/07/mapping-an-industrial-dispute.html#respond</comments>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Brian Prangle]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Sun, 16 Jul 2017 12:02:39 +0000</pubDate>
				<category><![CDATA[Use The Map]]></category>
		<guid isPermaLink="false">http://www.mappa-mercia.org/?p=1511</guid>

					<description><![CDATA[Birmingham is in the grip of an industrial dispute by binmen which is causing rubbish to pile up on the streets due to missed refuse collections. Needless to say this is causing much consternation amongst the citizens and businesses of &#8230; <a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2017/07/mapping-an-industrial-dispute.html">Continued</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>Birmingham is in the grip of an industrial dispute by binmen which is causing rubbish to pile up on the streets due to missed refuse collections. Needless to say this is causing much consternation amongst the citizens and businesses of the city and the local media and politicians. The causes of the dispute are long-running  and its resolution looks to be long-running also.</p>
<p>We do however have a <a href="https://mattcannon.carto.com/viz/06f57188-67c8-11e7-bb7e-0e98b61680bf/public_map">map of the effect of the dispute</a>, based on a release of data by the City Council of where residents have complained about missed refuse collections. The map was developed in Carto, and hence based on OSM data, by Matt Cannon who is digital development editor at the Birmingham Mail, one of our regional newspapers.</p>
<p>Are there any other examples of industrial dispute mapping?</p>
<div class="topic-intro"></div>
<p><a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="wp-image-1512 aligncenter" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute-300x152.png" alt="" width="341" height="173" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute-300x152.png 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute-768x389.png 768w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute-1024x519.png 1024w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2017/07/Bin-dispute.png 1916w" sizes="(max-width: 341px) 100vw, 341px" /></a></p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
