					<description><![CDATA[It may seem crazy talking about winter in the middle of August (unless of course you live in the southern hemisphere), however this weekend we updated our winter gritting map. The map shows which roads in the West Midlands are &#8230; <a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/2015/08/winter-preparedness.html">Continued</a>]]></description>
										<content:encoded><![CDATA[<p>It may seem crazy talking about winter in the middle of August (unless of course you live in the southern hemisphere), however this weekend we updated our <a href="/maps/gritting-map">winter gritting</a> map.</p>
<div id="attachment_1192" style="width: 376px" class="wp-caption aligncenter"><a href="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap.jpg"><img aria-describedby="caption-attachment-1192" decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-1192" src="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap.jpg" alt="Our brand new winter gritting map." width="366" height="367" srcset="https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap.jpg 366w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap-150x150.jpg 150w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap-300x300.jpg 300w, https://www.mappa-mercia.org/wp-content/uploads/2015/08/GrittingMap-250x251.jpg 250w" sizes="(max-width: 366px) 100vw, 366px" /></a><p id="caption-attachment-1192" class="wp-caption-text">Our brand new winter gritting map.</p></div>
<p>The map shows which roads in the West Midlands are gritted when it is cold and frosty. Up until now it has required us to manually update the data each time we wanted to refresh the map. As we continue to <a href="http://taginfo.openstreetmap.org.uk/tags/maintenance=gritting#overview" target="_blank">add</a> more winter gritting data to OpenStreetMap it makes sense to have the map auto-update. Following our own guide on how to make an <a href="/2014/09/creating-an-always-up-to-date-map.html" target="_blank">always up to date map</a> Andy Robinson developed a fantastic new winter gritting map which is <a href="/maps/gritting-map" target="_blank">available now</a>, with ample time to spare to winter 2015/16. Thanks Andy!</p>
]]></content:encoded>
					
